Release:	1
License:	GPL
Group:		X11/Applications/Games
Source0:	http://download.berlios.de/csboard/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	2c02bca491192be19273266781b6f18b
Source1:	%{name}.desktop
